strapiSongs.title: The Groove Gestapo
strapiSongs.lyrics:
Groove Gestapo house raid:

*This is the Groove Gestapo*
*Open up the door*
*Are you grooving in there*
strapiSongs.credits: Music by Victor Fisher of Reenchantment.
strapiSongs.description: This song was channeled from a strange dimension where Victor was a [glam rock](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glam_rock) guitarist during the 1970s.
